name: Busy Daisy
description: Nowadays girl are busy doing things. They pursue their dreams, some are run into a freedom and create their own version of success. People have their own vision to be success, but mostly in the end it's all about to be a better version of ourselves, to be the favorite person of ourselves. a more like-able person of us from us in the future. It's us versus us, it's you versus you, it's me versus me. Let's be busy to prepare a better us!.
